Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's Gaki no Tsukai: The 3rd installment of the Nostalgic Song Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:13.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Whenever ANYTHING happened they would make us all sing this song
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In this series, they drive while listening to songs they have memories about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,However today is a rainy day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:27.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's rare isn't it? There's usually no rain on Gaki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:28.93,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes, Gaki is rather lucky when it comes to weather
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.23,Hosei,,0,0,0,,On the "No Laughing Series" too
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:40.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,On "No Laughing", there's a lot of trade professionals right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There's some messed up folks in their ranks too
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Rain Men
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,280.149)}TN: Rain Man means someone unlucky who makes it rain when they show up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of rain men
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.06,Tanaka,,0,0,0,, Messed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:49.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be like 70 of them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.26,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:51.73,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There's like 100 staff members right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.86,Endo,,0,0,0,,I think even more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:53.86,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,More?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:56.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hamada, are your hemorrhoids alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I haven't gotten the surgery yet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:02.33,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Actually I too, I've got a straight up reserve army waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:04.41,Endo,,0,0,0,,Both of you have hemorrhoids?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.71,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,A straight up reserve army in waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:11.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If they break out, I might have to get surgery too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.30,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "a straight up reserve army"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They're not hemorrhoids right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:21.33,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Nah, they're almost, they're becoming like hemorrhoids
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:19.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh really
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:23.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,When you get tired they break out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:24.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:27.83,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So on "No Laughing" there must be a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:32.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I've heard there's actually a lot of hemorrhoid-comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:36.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I've heard a lot about hemorrhoid-comedians,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:39.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But the top of the pyramid is Hamada-san
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:44.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm at a rather low position
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:44.46,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Please raise your rank
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:47.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's so annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's so annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:53.43,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,TKO Kinoshita, and I think Kosugi from Black Mayonnaise too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:55.66,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah Kosugi too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I've heard when it gets really bad he places a napkin there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:00.66,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Kosugi is known for hemorrhoids
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:02.23,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His pants chafe him so he places a napkin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I thought "I wanna avoid that"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:08.33,Hosei,,0,0,0,,They say it looks like the crest of a chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:09.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,Woah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No no, that's a different type
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:13.41,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They're an anal fistula\N{\rEndo} Anal fistula?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:16.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They're not the same as piles or fissures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They happen in a different place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:20.46,Endo,,0,0,0,,Seperate from the anus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.46,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:23.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes, in inside the anus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:26.33,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's a hole in a different place,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.83,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Inside the anus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:29.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:33.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So there's like a tear there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.43,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Around the anus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.43,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,Why does that happen? Lack of hygine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's pretty rude
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.91,Endo,,0,0,0,,Well I do think it's rude, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.91,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's not why idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:48.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's cause they worked hard for Yoshimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:52.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's cause they worked hard to grow Yoshimoto from a tiny little agency
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san. Today we're on a drive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:03:02.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Last time we listened to everyone's nostalgic songs, but this time is different Matsumoto-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.53,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:13.21,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This time, everyone will record themselves at home, singing the song acapella by themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:20.31,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Recording using those nostalgic cassette tapes, really singing all by ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:24.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They gave us really difficult homework this time didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For this drive, they'll listen to acapella renditions of songs they recorded by themselves at home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Because of this digital age, listen to my analog recorded song"! Music Memory Drive Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.33,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So everyone sang a song they liked,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well speaking of songs we liked Matsumoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.03,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Most of us recorded 4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did 4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's true, I did too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.13,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Look at this please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.76,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,There's so many
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:54.91,Hosei,,0,0,0,,They gave me the big one, the case is different
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.91,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,The case is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:58.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is that from a past first date?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:02.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,He's very enthusiastic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's very enthusiasitc
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.93,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Someone put a tape in when we get on the highway
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.73,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Should the driver put his in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:12.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah should I start then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Let's listen now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Even putting the casette in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.50,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Very nostalgic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.56,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It was nostalgic recording it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:19.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough to make you die....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So serious all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffering and Sadness, Two or One of those feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.93,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is Nagabuchi Tsuyoshi right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, from here or there, burdens themselves with it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,Stay Dream, it's a famous song
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:47.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's not a single right? It's from an album
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.23,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes, from an album
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.33,Endo,,0,0,0,,The album Stay Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.00,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes I've heard Stay Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you sit down and try to block, the answer is Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.23,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He's good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.43,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough to blow it away
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger or Frustation, one or two of those things
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:11.25,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We have to listen to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.23,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's what this episode is about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:17.33,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,This is what it's supposed be like
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.73,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be like this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.63,Hosei,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:23.93,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We're not saying this song is bad, but you could have picked a more upbeat song for the first one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:30.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It may be a famous song, but maybe something more up-tempo would be better
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's true, actually
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so glum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.23,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,The voice is really coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:40.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You're at least singing loudly. You were by yourself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:43.73,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's true, I did this in the living room in the evening I think. Around 5pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.83,Endo,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be bad to sing so loudly at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:53.18,Endo,,0,0,0,,So I did it in the evening
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all stuck in this endless maze
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.86,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He's got the voice down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:05.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Did you...Look at the lyrics while singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.66,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was looking at the lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.95,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:18.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,And it's raining too...I'm gonna get depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.66,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It's a bad atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:23.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah it's over now. That was Nagabuchi-san's Stay Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:26.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,When I was in high school and doing my best playing baseball,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:34.10,Endo,,0,0,0,,It was my senpai's last match ever, and we lost, because of my mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:39.10,Endo,,0,0,0,,So when I was really down about it, like "I really messed up"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:47.46,Endo,,0,0,0,,That senpai brought a tape to me, and said "Listen to this". And it was Nagabuchi's Stay Dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:51.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,He said "Listen to this, and do your best again"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:53.63,Endo,,0,0,0,,And I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You cried?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:57.03,Endo,,0,0,0,,I cried, as expected
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.93,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It was your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:06:59.93,Endo,,0,0,0,,It was my fault after all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:04.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,I felt bad about it, and this song expressed that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.93,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough to make you die....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.53,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Enough already
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I said enough
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.46,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Let's listen a bit more
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:23.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,We're listening after my story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.83,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I thought you told him to play it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:29.89,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah, so we listen to it again taking to that story into account? ... I, I think I've heard it enough times
