Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Let's listen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:07.33,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You recorded this in Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:09.30,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I did this in Osaka, in my house, while the kids were at school
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The cheap sake I drank last night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Listen ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:16.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the cheap gin that gave me this headache
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,Be a director!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Be a director!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's copying Endo's kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,The vibe is the same
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bring a hot coffee to me in bed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(420,774)}Asa no Sillouhette - Igarashi Hiroaki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My white shirt hanging over your shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What do you guys think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:43.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This half-assed impression he's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't be gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I think he got it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.38,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's not supposed be an impression
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:48.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be you singing acapella
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to say "Goodbye"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like the basics I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.56,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It was a good thing you said that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:54.90,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Oh really? I'm singing normally though
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.70,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,No no no no
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Listen to it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does a man try to get a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.90,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.53,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He is good at this though
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.53,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell me your telephone number
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But still this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause I know too well how sad the end of love is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is a less well known song right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:23.30,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes, from the album Sand Castle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:30.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But like, a more famous song could be better
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,But I have memories of this song
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.85,Endo,,0,0,0,,When are these memories from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:39.90,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Theyr're really from, when I was in Osaka, before I came to Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:47.20,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Well it's exactly as the song says, "The gin I drank last night" and then "My head hurts" the next day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.87,Hosei,,0,0,0,,And the exact same thing happened to me while I was listening to this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:57.35,Hosei,,0,0,0,,And the girl I was dating at the time, well I didn't really drink coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:06.25,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I got her to bring me tea, while she had my white shirt hanging off my shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.20,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I got really turned on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You got turned on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.06,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:15.50,Hosei,,0,0,0,,She was wearing just my shirt, my oversized shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I'll go then
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:21.55,Hamada,,0,0,0,,A woman, something a bit more cheerful
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:26.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,All we've had are sad songs sung by men
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.15,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Right, of course, I apologise
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:29.55,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We're on a drive after all
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.90,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I thought my song would be good because it's raining
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah the mood right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,So Hamada-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after we kiss, don't say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:43.35,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Your voice is so quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.50,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Sakurada Junko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I might break out in tears, that's how much my heart is shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:49.75,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Hold on, this song?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(603.6,743.6)}Hajimete no Dekigoto (The first event) - Sakurada Junko
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:11:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't care, I do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.20,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.75,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's singing like he's about to die
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:04.45,Endo,,0,0,0,,Like he's about to die, his last words
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah really
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an act big enough to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His voice is so quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.55,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,It really is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been pretending to be mature, following you all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:15.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I couldn't really get my voice out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's a woman's song after all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:20.20,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He's not singing in the correct key
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:22.25,Endo,,0,0,0,,I thought this song was more passionate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:29.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I was singing right after I woke up, so my voice was still gravely
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.90,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I see, you weren't prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The overwhelming tears make me dizzy, and I don't get angry because I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:36.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why did you sing first thing in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:44.25,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You were being too considerate to your wife
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.10,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No no no
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.45,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You should really loudly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.70,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Was your wife sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:53.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You should sing loud enough to make your wife barge into the room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This was the song of our first idol
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.85,Hosei,,0,0,0,,This is one of her most famous songs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:02.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So Tanaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:13.07,Hosei,,0,0,0,,How should I say, "The First Experience?", sorry right "The first event"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.95,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,This one please
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.45,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you Tanaka seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:14.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda worried about Tanaka-san's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:19.95,Endo,,0,0,0,,Honestly, he's not very good at singing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.95,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Tanaka is a bad singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.25,Endo,,0,0,0,,And it's acapella too
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You could count happiness on one hand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.15,Endo,,0,0,0,,Eh? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.85,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I think Endo knows this one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You need more than both hands to count sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is kinda creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(552,754.8)}Sachiko - Banba Hirofumi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.40,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's not creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.65,Endo,,0,0,0,,Like a haunted tape
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Isn't this too quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how clean your heart is, you can still believe in ugly things
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.85,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you cry now, one day this will be a funny story
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Man you're so quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:14.10,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's hard to sing, even though I picked this song
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko, I remember that street
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.07,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachiko, live on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:21.75,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It really does
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.70,Hosei,,0,0,0,,His voice really tapers off at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a sad love story, when you forget the laughing good times,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.15,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He SUCKS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.55,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's too quiet, and he sucks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:29.15,Endo,,0,0,0,,You really are super quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:32.15,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He hasn't improved at all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.65,Hosei,,0,0,0,,See his voice is breaking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay by your side until you remember
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:36.35,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Hosei-san has told me that many times
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.75,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's been consistently bad so far
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:44.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Just pick a song with a key you can sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:48.05,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's true, I tried so many times
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:54.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why did you go and make up rules for yourself for no reason, just sing acapella
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:14:00.00,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Back in Year 2 or 3 of middle school, at an event for appreciating music
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:09.10,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,At the neighbourhood Toyonaka Civic Centre, Bunba Hirofumi-san actually performed this song live
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:16.70,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,So that was the first time I ever saw a professional singer live
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:20.90,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was really amazed by a pro singer's awesomeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.85,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.85,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,His presence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:26.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That was really impactful to me. Even now this song,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:30.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It was a popular song
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.10,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I can't forget this song
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:33.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Man you suck at singing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:34.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san, your turn please
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:39.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be, this one, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:43.31,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You suck at singing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, what nostalgic song will Matsumoto sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know of it, Yokohama Harbour
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:55.25,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ah yes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What kind of memories do you have of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:00.55,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a really old song?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.55,Hamada,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.95,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh you know this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.95,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I've heard the first phrase before
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.45,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No no listen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,His voice is all over the place
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream sprinkled in the lights of Isezaki
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572.4,738.8)}Isezakichou Blues - Mina Aoe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:18.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This part, from here\
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.70,Hosei,,0,0,0,,His voice is breaking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Passionate love,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dooby Dooby Dooby Doo-ahhh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The light stops
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.05,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So goddamn passionate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.55,Endo,,0,0,0,,Very passionate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You guys should be this passionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Like a dad singing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.35,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My memories of this are with my father
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:46.95,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My dad loved Aoe Mina
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.95,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,This is Aoe Mina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.15,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My dad liked her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:56.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,At the time, she had slightly blonde hair, and had that erotic atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:16:03.55,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So my dad would always get excited about Aoe Mina, and my mom would get pissed off
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:06.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I thought "So creepy"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:11.35,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My excited dad creeped me out, and my angry mother creeped me out too
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:15.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I really hated it when I was a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.70,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:19.15,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Your mom's jealousy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:22.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My mom would go "What is that crap? So indecent!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:27.35,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Don't show your spouse those feelings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:30.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I would say mine was the most powerful singing today
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No no no
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:34.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,Well there were other powerful ones
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.65,Hosei,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:41.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What do you think? We've done one rotation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.95,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yama-chan are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:46.85,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:50.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We haven't listened to a cheerful song yet
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.70,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The harbor light changes in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.35,Endo,,0,0,0,,You're going at max tension right away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, the first seagull flew
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.20,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.35,Endo,,0,0,0,,Your voice is really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He got us with this one
